You spent your whole life in service to the gods of Asgard. You
died an honorable death. You earned your place in the halls of
Valhalla. But when you knocked on its gates to receive your final
reward, none answered. Odin has turned his back on your people. He
underestimates the Viking spirit. He underestimates you. Force
their hand as you lead your people past the dangers waiting on
Valhalla Hills and fight to prove your honor, your strength, your
worthiness.

For more info go to : http://www.gog.com/game/valhalla_hills
